In [4]:
def strip_rdf_graph(rdf_graph: Graph, n_nodes: int):
    lits = [node for node in rdf_graph.all_nodes() if isinstance(node, Literal)]
    for lit in lits:
        rdf_graph.remove((lit,None,None))
        rdf_graph.remove((None,lit,None))
        rdf_graph.remove((None,None,lit))
    
    undesired_nodes = [node for node in rdf_graph.all_nodes()][n_nodes:]
    for node in undesired_nodes:
        rdf_graph.remove((node,None,None))
        rdf_graph.remove((None,node,None))
        rdf_graph.remove((None,None,node))
    
    return rdf_graph
